        <updateDate>2023-04-07T11:19:18Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Korematsu-Takai Civil Liberties Protection Act of 2023 </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the detention or imprisonment of an individual based solely on an actual or perceived protected characteristic of the individual. The term <i>protected characteristic</i> includes each of the following: race, ethnicity, national origin, religion, sex, gender identity, sexual orientation, disability, and any additional characteristic that the Department of Justice determines to be a protected characteristic.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
